  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Atranta.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/50px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/75px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/100px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Armistead Vance</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/50px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/75px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/100px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Kingship\" title=\"Kingship\">King</a> (presumably)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance\" title=\"House Vance\">House Vance</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Armistead Vance</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance\" title=\"House Vance\">House Vance</a> and the mightiest of the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andal</a> warlords that <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">invaded</a> the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Armistead_Vance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Armistead was presumably one of the seven Andal kings who defeated <a href=\"/index.php/Tristifer_IV_Mudd\" title=\"Tristifer IV Mudd\">Tristifer IV Mudd</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rivers_and_the_Hills\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the Rivers and the Hills\">King of the Rivers and the Hills</a>. Afterward he gained the allegiance of <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully_(father_of_Axel)\" title=\"Edmure Tully (father of Axel)\">Edmure Tully</a> and his sons. Armistead granted Edmure's son <a href=\"/index.php/Axel_Tully\" title=\"Axel Tully\">Axel</a> lands at the juncture of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Tumblestone\" title=\"Tumblestone\">Tumblestone</a>, where Lord Axel raised <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Armistead_Vance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands: House Tully.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183000\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.244 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 505/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10428/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5770/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 638/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 994/5000000 bytes\nLua